    <title>快速排序</title>
    <link href="/2021/04/08/quick_sort/"/>
    <url>/2021/04/08/quick_sort/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>快排思想：<br>    partition从两端进行。 每次划分将数组划分两部分，再各自递归划分。每次划分都确定一个标志位的位置。</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-comment">//划分</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">partition</span><span class="hljs-params">(vector&amp; vec, <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> start, <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> end)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = start,<br>        j = end+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<br>        v = start;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(vec[++i] &lt; vec[v])<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i == end)    <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(vec[--j] &gt; vec[v])<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(j == start)  <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i &gt;= j)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        std::<span class="hljs-built_in">swap</span>(vec[i],vec[j]);<br>    &#125;<br>    std::<span class="hljs-built_in">swap</span>(vec[v],vec[j]);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> j;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//递归快排</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">qk_sort</span><span class="hljs-params">(vector&amp; vec, <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> start, <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> end)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(start &gt;= end)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> mid = <span class="hljs-built_in">partition</span>(vec,start,end);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">qk_sort</span>(vec,start,mid<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">qk_sort</span>(vec,mid+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,end);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
